<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to Bank of Saturn – ₦100,000 Bonus</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2540 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 48px 40px 36px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: #0a2540;
    }

    .bonus-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
      border: 2px solid #60a5fa;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      margin: 32px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .bonus-amount {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      margin: 12px 0 8px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #1d4ed8;
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 24px 0 16px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.25);
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #1e40af;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.35);
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #0a2540;
      color: #a5b4fc;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #60a5fa;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 12px;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Bank of Saturn</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="greeting">Welcome to Bank of Saturn, <%= fullName %>!</h2>

      <p>Thank you for choosing us — we're excited to have you on board.</p>
      <p>At Bank of Saturn, we believe banking should be simple, secure, and rewarding. That's why we've automatically
        credited your new account with:</p>

      <div class="bonus-box">
        <p style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #1e40af;">Your Welcome Bonus</p>
        <div class="bonus-amount">₦100,000</div>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #1e40af;">Account Creation Bonus</p>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">
        Your account (<%= accountNumber %>) is now ready — log in and explore everything we offer:
      </p>

      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">
          Go to Your Dashboard →
        </a>
      </p>

      <p style="margin: 32px 0 0; font-size: 15px;">
        Start today:
      </p>
      <ul style="margin: 12px 0 32px 20px; padding-left: 0; font-size: 15px;">
        <li>Check your balance and transaction history</li>
        <li>Deposit funds and start saving</li>
        <li>Pay bills and transfer money instantly</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #4b5563;">
        Questions? Our support team is available 24/7 — just reply to this email or visit our help center.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2026 Bank of Saturn. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="margin: 12px 0 0;">
        <a href="<%= supportUrl %>">Help Center</a> •
        <a href="<%= privacyUrl %>">Privacy Policy</a> •
        <a href="<%= termsUrl %>">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>